sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Code
    participant Exp as AI4RAGExperiment
    participant MPS as ModelsPreSelector
    participant SS as SearchSpace
    participant GAM as GAMOptimizer
    participant Template as SimpleRAGTemplate
    participant Chunker as LangChainChunker
    participant Emb as OGX Embeddings<br/>HTTPS / API Key
    participant VS as OGX Vector Store<br/>HTTPS / API Key
    participant FM as OGX Chat Completions<br/>HTTPS / API Key
    participant ChromaDB as ChromaDB<br/>In-memory
    participant Eval as UnitxtEvaluator
    participant EH as EventHandler<br/>(KFP / Local)

    Note over User,EH: Flow 1: RAG Optimization Experiment

    User->>Exp: search(search_space, documents)
    Exp->>SS: generate valid combinations<br/>(constraint-based pruning)
    SS-->>Exp: filtered parameter grid

    opt Models Pre-Selection (MPS)
        Note over MPS,ChromaDB: Flow 2: Pre-selects top-N model pairs
        Exp->>MPS: run(all model pairs)
        loop For each embedding + FM pair
            MPS->>Emb: create embeddings (sample data)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / API Key
            Emb-->>MPS: embedding vectors
            MPS->>ChromaDB: insert & query (in-memory)
            ChromaDB-->>MPS: retrieved chunks
            MPS->>FM: chat.completions.create<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / API Key
            FM-->>MPS: generated answers
            MPS->>Eval: evaluate(predictions, references)
            Eval-->>MPS: scores (correctness, faithfulness)
        end
        MPS-->>Exp: top-N model pairs
    end

    Note over Exp,EH: Main Optimization Loop

    loop For each trial (random then GAM-guided)
        Exp->>GAM: suggest next configuration
        GAM-->>Exp: parameter combination

        Exp->>Template: instantiate RAG pattern

        Template->>Chunker: chunk documents<br/>(recursive text split)
        Chunker-->>Template: document chunks

        Template->>Emb: embeddings.create(chunks)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / API Key
        Emb-->>Template: embedding vectors

        Template->>VS: vector_stores.create + vector_io.insert<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / API Key
        VS-->>Template: indexed

        Template->>Emb: embeddings.create(queries)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / API Key
        Emb-->>Template: query embeddings

        Template->>VS: vector_io.query(similarity search)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / API Key
        VS-->>Template: retrieved context chunks

        Template->>FM: chat.completions.create(context + query)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / API Key
        FM-->>Template: generated answer

        Template-->>Exp: RAG pattern result

        Exp->>Eval: evaluate(predictions, references)<br/>In-process
        Eval-->>Exp: scores with confidence intervals

        Exp->>GAM: update model with observation
        Exp->>EH: emit pattern result
    end

    Exp->>EH: emit experiment complete
    Exp-->>User: ExperimentResults<br/>(best pattern + all scores)
